  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine response to pain in Alzheimer's disease.We plan to
      study the effect of diffuse noxious inhibitory controls(counterirritation phenomenon)and the
      autonomic nervous system reaction(reflected by the heart rate) in Alzheimer's disease. The
      study's hypothesis is that pain perception and autonomic nervous system reaction are altered
      in Alzheimer's disease.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
